 enroll for graduate work in the school of earth sciences must be qualified for graduate standing in the university and must be accepted by one of the school's four departments or e iper we encourage you to explore our departments and programs and to contact individual faculty members in your areas of interest learn more for additional information pleae contact roni holeton assistant dean for academic affairs at 650 721 3383 or roni stanford edu stanford university school of earth sciences 397 panama mall ca 94305 2210 mitchell building 101 tel 650 723 2544 2012 stanford university related resources employment opportunities hartley conference center health and safety computing resources room resources how can we help maps & directions stanfordwho office of the registrar contact us connect to earth sciences facebook itunes u twitter youtube
